    If the file has absolute path:

    new File("C:/Users/User1/Desktop/Logs/test.txt")


`BufferedReader` prefer over`FileReader` to enhance performance(stores data into a buffer line by
line).

- try with resources

    Automatically close  streams, we don’t need finally block.

    // try-with-resources ilə axınlar avtomatik bağlanacaq
            try (FileReader fileReader = new FileReader(fileName);
                 BufferedReader bufferedReader = new BufferedReader(fileReader)) {

